{topic:Trial Point}{F:0}{Rule:0}{Picture:R,Logo}
This is an example topic used to try out cross reference following. When you have read this text you can get back to where you were when you followed the cross reference by using the Back Trace option. To do this, click select on the back trace icon in the toolbox or click {B:MENU} over this window and select the Back Trace option from the Tools sub-menu (the back trace icon looks like this: {Picture:I,trace} ).
